name: bigquerydatatransfer
name_pretty: BigQuery Data Transfer Service V1 API
ruby-cloud-description: Schedules queries and transfers external data from SaaS applications to Google BigQuery on a regular basis. Note that google-cloud-bigquery-data_transfer-v1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-bigquery-data_transfer instead. See the readme for more details.
